<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/169601ALVRHMPBCVCJMJHTSJJHHNKHJVM>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "2026 CO Dance Team Showcase";
  schema:description """
	<h1>Creative Outlet’s annual competitive dance showcase bursts to life with unstoppable energy, showcasing the passion, power, and artistry of dancers who’ve spent the season pushing their limits. </h1><span><br/></span>From heart pounding high energy hip hop to breathtaking acro and lyrical, each routine lights up the stage with fierce technique, bold storytelling, and the unmistakable spirit that defines CO. Families, friends, and fans are swept into a whirlwind of rhythm, emotion, and show stopping talent as our dancers celebrate a year of growth, grit, and unforgettable performances. It’s more than a recital—it’s a celebration of creativity, community, and the magic that happens when dedication meets the spotlight.
""";
  schema:startDate "2026-06-11T18:30:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
