<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/174001AVGNLQTLCJCDRPHLTLLMCSMJLHR>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "2026 Footsteps Dance Recital";
  schema:description """
	<h1>Creative Outlet’s annual Footsteps dance recital brings together the joy, discipline and imagination of our recreational and demi-competitive dancers. </h1><span><br/></span>Each routine highlights a unique blend of artistry and growth. Audiences are treated to a dynamic journey through creative recreational pieces, elegant ballet works, and high energy competitive numbers, all reflecting the dedication and spirit that define our studio. It’s a heartwarming, inspiring showcase of every dancer’s progress and passion as they shine under the lights.
""";
