<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/169801ADKHSPCDPNCSVSLSBGGVRMRGSPC>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "2026 Little Steps \"Alice!\"";
  schema:description """
	<h1>Step into a world of wonder as our dancers ages 2 to 7 bring Alice in Wonderland to life in the sweetest, most enchanting way.</h1><span><br/></span>From tiny Alices taking their first curious steps to lively White Rabbits, tap dancing Cheshire Cats, and acrobatic Tea Party guests, each performance invites the audience deeper into a story filled with imagination and charm. With bright costumes, joyful movement, and the pure delight that only young dancers can bring to the stage, this recital celebrates creativity, confidence and magic.
""";
