  schema:priceCurrency "CAD" .

<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/93201APSNKTSHQMVPMTLQPVBVVLTQCRLN>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "A Holly Jolly Christmas";
  schema:description """
	<h1>Returning to the HUB Theatre this festive season, Zachary Stevenson is ready to light up the stage with his wildly popular signature holiday concert, reimagined for 2025!</h1><span><br/></span>Combining beloved Christmas classics with some of the biggest hits of the 1950s and 60s, A Holly Jolly Christmas is a toe-tapping, heart-warming, rock'n'roll extravaganza that is sure to get you in the holiday spirit.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>\"The epitome of effortless cool Zachary Stevenson's gorgeous voice and a star-quality stage presence.\" - Mark Robbins, Vancouver Presents<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Internationally-acclaimed for playing the title role in over ten productions of Buddy: The Buddy Holly Story, and cheekily coined as “A Dead Ringer for Dead Singers” (Victoria Times Colonist); Zachary Stevenson has brought his unforgettable voice, award-winning persona, and uncanny ability to channel the likes of Buddy Holly, Jerry Lee Lewis, Hank Williams (and more) across the globe, thrilling audiences across Canada, the US, Netherlands, and UK. Chilliwack audiences are in for an evening of world-class entertainment from this incredible performer.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>“If you don’t like him, you don’t like much of anybody!” (Chris Jones, Chicago Tribune)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Brimming with vintage charm and featuring an all-star band, playing 100% live - just like the good ol' days - A Holly Jolly Christmas is the one Holly-day concert you won’t want to miss!
""";
  schema:startDate "2025-12-06T19:30:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
  schema:image <https://system.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/files/57ba02c4-cf8b-47c0-8530-49f22dcd8d06.jpg>;
  schema:location <https://spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/location/4201ASVGBHHRTVLQBSRVKDQCKNHHDCTSJ>;
