  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "A Traditional Christmas 2025";
  schema:description """
	<h1>All your favourite classic Christmas songs in a single, remarkable concert! </h1><span><br/></span>Grab your friends and family for A Traditional Christmas! This special holiday concert with the Chilliwack Metropolitan Orchestra featuring your favourite classic and contemporary Christmas songs! With some lovely choral selections to accompany their orchestral pieces, the Chilliwack Metropolitan Orchestra blends the old with the new for a festive concert to get you in the holiday spirit!
""";
