  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Absinthe and the Green Fairy";
  schema:description """
	<h1>A cabaret soaked in desire. One dancer’s rise. One sip too far. Absinthe and the Green Fairy</h1><span><br/></span>In a decadent cabaret, a dancer rises toward fame — but the price of stardom comes steep. Seduced by the Green Fairy’s promises, Élise teeters between brilliance and ruin as reality blurs into dreams. Absinthe and the Green Fairy invites you to lose yourself in a world where every choice shimmers with danger — wand every sip could be your last.
""";
