<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/166201APDBMLKQLGPPHNRNSPRHKRJPPPQ>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Advent Messiah";
  schema:description """
	<h1>Experience the wonder of the Advent season with a heartfelt performance of Handel’s Messiah, presented by Cantare Super Orchestram, with outstanding soloists.</h1><span><br/></span>This intimate concert features the Advent portions of Messiah, capturing the hope and anticipation of the season, and includes the iconic Hallelujah Chorus—a moment of pure joy and power. Performed with historical authenticity and rich expression, this is a rare opportunity to hear Handel’s masterpiece in a beautifully intimate setting.
""";
