<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/102001AJMQLQRLPQBJDHKSMKHRJJQGBLS>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "ARRIVAL & DREAMS";
  schema:description """
	<h1>ARRIVAL, Canada's Tribute to ABBA, is an authentic sounding, six-piece tribute to Abba. </h1><span><br/></span>They perform in full costume and have been packing venues consistently around North America Celebrating 20 years! This band of elite musicians has played hundreds of shows in casinos, theatres, festivals and at corporate events, all around the world. Some of those places include Las Vegas, the Caribbean, Ontario Tours and across Western Canada including Pre-Olympic Vancouver 2010 performances. You will be amazed at how close Arrival, Canada’s Tribute to Abba sounds like the original Abba. That coupled with their high energy choreography and multi-media making this the show of all Abba Shows. Arrival takes you back in time, so you can experience this amazing music all over again!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h1>DREAMS – NORTH AMERICA’sS ULTIMATE TRIBUTE TO FLEETWOOD MAC, is an authentic sounding, six-piece LIVE Tribute to Fleetwood Mac Celebrating 20 Years.  </h1><span><br/></span>They perform in full costumes, replicating the actual styles worn by the original band. This band of professional musicians has set the standard consistently, playing hundreds of standing ovations shows in casinos, theatres, festivals and corporate events, all around the world. Some of those places include Las Vegas where they opened for the Original 3 Dog Night, the Dominican Republic and across Western Canada including the Pacific National Exhibition in Vancouver, and in the USA. From the precise vocals to their stage presence, it’s undeniable Dreams takes it to a whole new level.
""";
  schema:startDate "2026-04-25T19:30:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
  schema:image <https://system.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/files/adbb43cd-d768-4cdf-9dba-0abbd848f2f7.jpg>;
  schema:location <https://spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/location/4201ASVGBHHRTVLQBSRVKDQCKNHHDCTSJ>;
  schema:offers _:1290a8eb9d794355b3e34223272b36867465;
  schema:keywords "Tribute Band";
  schema:duration "PT60M";
  schema:endDate "2026-04-25T20:30:00"^^xsd:dateTime .

