<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/181201ASRVGRNHSCPQQRJBTSNDMVVRPDR>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Autumn Classics";
  schema:description """
	<h1>Experience an unforgettable evening of brilliance and charm as the Chilliwack Metropolitan Orchestra presents Autumn Classics.</h1><span><br/></span>The program opens with the sparkling wit of Rossini’s Overture to The Barber of Seville, accompanied by the elegance and youthful exuberance of Prokofiev’s Classical Symphony.  The evening’s centerpiece is Beethoven’s majestic Piano Concerto No. 1, featuring gifted local pianist Emily Jou, whose remarkable artistry and expressive playing have already captured the attention of audiences across the region. Join us for a celebration of timeless masterworks, vibrant orchestral colour, and the extraordinary talent of one of our community’s rising stars.
""";
