<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/142001AKSQSJSTQGPJNJVLGPKTPDNPVHC>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Baby Tyler";
  schema:description """
	<h1>Hansen turns anything and everything into a puppet and makes it funny.</h1><span><br/></span>Using everyday objects, her bare hands, and her legendary sense of surprise, the seasoned television puppeteer Ingrid Hansen (Fraggle Rock / Jim Henson Co. and Sesame Workshop) creates surreal and hilarious situations with her bare hands, miniature environments, and modeling clay. Stories in these tiny worlds are performed live and magnified by a video camera onto a huge screen. Let yourself be swept away into his miniature world for a delirious and surreal journey on the big screen as you follow the adventures of Baby Tyler. Standing just 25 cm tall, this mischievous little creature uses his cunning to overcome the many obstacles that punctuate his daily life in this world designed for grown-ups... For all ages AGE 5+. <span><br/></span>
""";
