<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/26801APBDSSBSQMVTPLPRDJQMMKCLMHMP>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Bad Moon Riders";
  schema:description """
	<h1>This Amazing CCR Tribute Concert returns to the Chilliwack in the HUB International Theatre!!</h1><span><br/></span>A night of incredible music and nostalgia as Bad Moon Riders pay tribute to the legendary band, Creedence Clearwater Revival (CCR). Bad Moon Riders, comprised of Members from BTO and Headpins, deliver ALL the hits, ALL night long. From \"Proud Mary\" to \"Bad Moon Rising\", to \"Fortunate Son\". You'll be singing ALL night Long!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Special Guest Opening Act. BCO, Canada's Tribute to Bachman Turner Overdrive, will be \"Takin care of Business\" & all the other BTO hits!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>19+ Event
""";
