  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Beaded Poppies";
  schema:description """
	Honour those who served on Remembrance Day and indigenous Veteran’s Day with a beaded poppy pin that you have personally handcrafted. Jenn Carman from Two Rose Beading will guide you through the process from laying the pattern, to stitching, and attaching the pin back. A portion of each registration will be donated to the Royal Canadian Legion and the Aboriginal Veterans Autochtones (Anavets)
""";
