<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/4127ACSLJSCGDCQGDJSRJBMMLJHPJCCCV>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Bellamy Brothers";
  schema:description """
	<h1>THE BELLAMY BROTHERS: THE LOVE STILL FLOWS…</h1><span><br/></span>Howard and David continue to prove that the trail they’ve ridden to fame has been as unique as their music itself—music that is now celebrating 40 years of success.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>The road that started on the pop music charts in the ‘70’s, took a winding turn into country music in the ‘80’s, paving the way for duos to come, such as Brooks & Dunn, Montgomery Gentry, Big & Rich, and previously—The Judds. But before the road forked into country, the musical odyssey of brothers Bellamy started creatively smoldering in their home state of Florida, before exploding nationally amidst the ’70’s pop music culture of L.A.
""";
  schema:startDate "2025-05-15T19:30:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
  schema:image <https://system.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/files/073554be-aeef-4156-b630-3bbf52d713b5.jpg>;
  schema:location <https://spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/location/4201ASVGBHHRTVLQBSRVKDQCKNHHDCTSJ>;
  schema:offers _:1290a8eb9d794355b3e34223272b36867508;
  schema:keywords "Music";
  schema:duration "PT120M";
  schema:endDate "2025-05-15T21:30:00"^^xsd:dateTime .

_:1290a8eb9d794355b3e34223272b36867508 a schema:AggregateOffer;
  schema:lowPrice "70.95";
  schema:priceCurrency "CAD" .

<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/48601ARPGPBJPBBJPGRVPTHVCMTBCKDRT>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Beyond the Sky";
  schema:description """
	<h1>Beyond the Sky: An Intimate Evening with Chris Hadfield</h1><span><br/></span>As part of our 15th Anniversary celebrations, the Chilliwack Cultural Centre is proud to present an unforgettable evening with Canadian astronaut, best-selling author, and musician Chris Hadfield.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Join us for a captivating journey beyond the stars as Colonel Hadfield shares his extraordinary experiences from space exploration to life’s most meaningful moments here on Earth. With his signature warmth, humour, and insight, Hadfield will inspire with stories of resilience, curiosity, and pushing the limits of possibility.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>But the evening doesn’t stop with storytelling — Chris Hadfield will also showcase his musical talents, performing songs that blend his love for music and space, including selections he famously recorded aboard the International Space Station.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>This unique event celebrates wonder, creativity, and discovery — core values of our Cultural Centre’s mission over the past 15 years. Be part of this milestone night where science, music, and imagination collide.<span><br/></span>
""";
  schema:startDate "2025-09-25T19:30:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
  schema:image <https://system.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/files/0d8913f9-e06b-4af8-b11e-e64c3adfbc40.jpg>;
  schema:location <https://spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/location/4201ASVGBHHRTVLQBSRVKDQCKNHHDCTSJ>;
  schema:offers _:1290a8eb9d794355b3e34223272b36867509;
  schema:duration "PT60M";
  schema:endDate "2025-09-25T20:30:00"^^xsd:dateTime .

_:1290a8eb9d794355b3e34223272b36867509 a schema:AggregateOffer;
  schema:lowPrice "75.0";
  schema:priceCurrency "CAD" .

<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/78402AGQLKTBGRKVPRMLDSQHJDMKJPLLB>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Birds of a Feather";
  schema:description """
	As we flock together over the next few weeks, we will let our files take flight and carve beautiful Brazilian bird heads. We will peck away at learning about the tools we are using, fun facts about soapstone, and soar through techniques and polishing. Turn your bird head into a pen holder, feather holder or an incense holder. Let your bird take perch on your favourite shelf or mantle. This is a four (4) week course.
""";
  schema:startDate "2025-11-02T13:30:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
  schema:location <https://spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/location/4201ASVGBHHRTVLQBSRVKDQCKNHHDCTSJ>;
