<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/132801ALNSRCRGCVGDNPBCVMGSRLBKJTR>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Brent Butt in Chilliwack";
  schema:description """
	<h1>Brent Butt in Chilliwack</h1><span><br/></span>Brent Butt has long been considered one of the funniest people in Canada, with a career in stand-up comedy that stretches into five decades, including numerous appearances at major festivals in multiple countries and being voted Best Male Stand-Up in Canada by his peers in the profession. He also created and starred in two successful sitcoms – CORNER GAS (“Funniest Show on TV” as voted by TV Guide Readers, currently in 60 countries) and HICCUPS (multiple Leo and Writers Guild Awards).
""";
