<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/180601ASMQKJHDVSJPGGDPPMVKMGTDJMG>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Brian Minter";
  schema:description """
	<h1>Join Brian Minter for an inspiring look at how to keep your garden vibrant and engaging through the cooler months. </h1><span><br/></span>This session explores the best perennials, shrubs, and seasonal plants that provide colour, texture, and structure throughout fall and winter, proving that the garden does not have to go dormant when the temperatures drop.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>You will also learn about designing and creating stunning winter container gardens with hardy plants that thrive in colder conditions. Brian will share practical tips and creative ideas to help you extend the beauty of your outdoor spaces all season long.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Perfect for gardeners of all levels looking to add year-round interest and make the most of every season.
""";
