<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/55001AMSBLSDPDNMRVSMJKRHLNGCNQBMH>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Burning Mom";
  schema:description """
	<h1>Comedy and self-realization come together in this one-woman play – join us for the ride!</h1><span><br/></span>After the sudden death of her husband, Dorothy realizes life is too short to delay your aspirations. Seizing life by the horns, she decides to take their RV and fulfill his retirement dreams: going to Burning Man. It’s just a 21-hour drive to the Nevada desert for a weeklong culture festival with no plumbing or AC – how hard can it be? Burning Mom is a hilarious yet poignant tale about self-discovery and how art, everlasting roads, and human connection propel us along the way.
""";
  schema:startDate "2026-02-04T19:30:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
