<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/187001ANRDTDJNVTPHPBSPTNVHPHNMPQL>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Canadian Steam";
  schema:description """
	<h1>Straight from the land of moose, maple, and modesty, Canadian Steam is a high-energy blend of music, ridiculous comedy, and mildly sexy lumberjack charm. </h1><span><br/></span>It’s a show for everyone! Girls and guys hang onto your toques get ready for some Canadian comedy!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>These flannel-clad heartthrobs have been officially dispatched by the Ministry of Sexy™ yes, that’s totally a thing, on a national mission to prove that Canada’s greatest export isn’t hockey, or maple syrup. It’s sexiness. Because nothing is sexier than being hilarious.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Armed with silly serenades, dangerously enthusiastic dance numbers, and some of the most average dad bods this side of the Rockies, these lumberjacks are cranking up the charm one town at a time.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>But here’s the twist: at the end of the night, YOU hold the power. Your cheers, your laughter, and your votes determine whether these Mildly Sexy Lumberjacks earn the Official Stamp of Sexy, representing Canada on the international stage and proving to the world that our number one export is sexiness, because we’re hilarious. Succeed? They go home as heroes. Fail? They’ll be politely asked to hang up their flannel and return to their log cabins.
""";
  schema:startDate "2026-10-02T19:30:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
  schema:location <https://spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/location/4201ASVGBHHRTVLQBSRVKDQCKNHHDCTSJ>;
  schema:offers _:1290a8eb9d794355b3e34223272b36867525;
  schema:keywords "Comedy";
  schema:duration "PT60M";
  schema:endDate "2026-10-02T20:30:00"^^xsd:dateTime .

_:1290a8eb9d794355b3e34223272b36867525 a schema:AggregateOffer;
  schema:lowPrice "26.0";
  schema:priceCurrency "CAD" .

<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/76001ACNQBDSGGTSVDMCVRMLGHGQHVKLH>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Canadian Steam 2025";
  schema:description """
	<h1>Canadian Steam: A Music & Comedy Show with Mildly Sexy Lumberjacks</h1><span><br/></span>They’re Polite, But Not Tonight!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>It’s Whose Line Is It Anyway? meets the Great White North.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Straight from the land of moose, maple, and modesty, Canadian Steam is a high-energy blend of musical comedy, ridiculous improv, and medium-hot lumberjack charm. These flannel-clad heartthrobs have been officially dispatched by the Ministry of Sexy™ (yes, that’s totally a thing) to prove that Canada isn’t just nice, it’s irresistibly hilarious.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Armed with maple syrup, smooth serenades, and some of the most average bods this side of the Rockies, these lumberjacks are on a national mission to crank up the charm and bring the funny - one town at a time.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>But here’s the twist: YOU decide if they’ve earned the Official Stamp of Sexy at the end of the night. Your cheers, your laughter, your votes.  If not? They'll be politely asked to hang up their flannel and go back to their log cabins in shame.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Don’t miss this incredible night brought to you from the award-winning minds at The Comedy Department (TripAdvisor Traveller's Choice Winners.)
""";
  schema:startDate "2025-11-08T19:30:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
