  schema:description """
	<h1>December 5th Scheduled Comedians!</h1>• Ivan Decker (Netflix, Conan, Juno Winner)<span><br/></span>• Syd Bosel (Canada’s Got Talent, CBC Debaters)<span><br/></span>• Alex Carr (National Touring Comedian & Radio Host)<span><br/></span>+ more performer(s) to be announced!<span><br/></span>*lineup subject to change due to unforeseen circumstance <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>“Back by popular demand, Jokers Canada returns to our city with a FRESH LINEUP of touring headliners & Canada’s funniest pro comedians. Safe money by purchasing online in advance”.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Dec 5th performers to be announced. Follow @jokerscanada for more information.” 18+ event: Please be aware of possible adult languange & content
