<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/90201APGBLJVMBRTQMNBCPTNCKVRLMPBT>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Chilliwack Rock Choir";
  schema:description """
	<h1>Get ready to rock!</h1><span><br/></span>The Chilliwack Rock Choir is back to crank your favourites up to 11! This isn’t just any choir performance — backed by a live band, they deliver classic rock anthems with the raw energy and excitement of a full-blown rock show. Feel the powerful vocals and infectious rhythms that will have you singing along and dancing in your seat.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>All proceeds will support Chilliwack Community Services, so bring your family, friends, and your best rock ‘n’ roll spirit for a night of music, community, and celebration!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Don’t miss your chance to experience the thrill of a live rock show with one of the largest and most spirited choirs in town. Join us for an evening that will leave you buzzing long after the final note — grab your tickets now!​
""";
