<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/3624ASLKJMDRVKJPNTPBRMCTGKNRCCDKQ>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Citizen Hurricane!";
  schema:description """
	<h1>Citizen Hurricane! It’s a Rock’n’Roll comedy show!</h1>Part Stand Up – Part Improv – Part Music – ALL COMEDY<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>David and Ken are Citizen Hurricane: an improvised comedy and concert inspired by audience suggestions.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>It’s Tenacious D meets Adam Sandler meets the Flight of the Conchords with a dash of Whose Line is it Anyway.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Have you seen the Comic Strippers and the Comedy Department then you’ve seen these guys.  You’ve probably seen them on TV and heard them on CBC’s the Debaters. They’ve been improvising and touring comedy for over 20 years so get ready for a night you’ll never forget!
""";
