  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Clay Date Night";
  schema:description """
	Looking for something different to do on a Friday night? Bring your date, partner, friend, or family member out to the Clay Studio! Let our instructor takes you through a couple of handbuilding projects using a variety of techniques and equipment. Your creations will be glazed, and fired for you and you will be notified when they are ready to be picked up in a couple of weeks. All date nights are suitable for folks with no clay experience. We welcome all couples/partner groups.
""";
