<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/143201ALKQBKGTBLRTMBHLJSQRRLDCPNK>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Comic Strippers";
  schema:description """
	<h1>The award-winning improv comedians are back with a brand-new show, bigger laughs, bolder energy, and even quicker wits.</h1><span><br/></span>The Comic Strippers are a fictitious male revue troupe played by some of Canada’s top improvisers, delivering a fast paced, high energy comedy spectacle that gleefully spoofs classic strip show clichés. Fueled by audience suggestions, the cast banters, sings, grooves, and “dances” through a completely unscripted night where anything can happen. Packed with audience interaction and razor-sharp improv, the cast banters, sings, grooves, and “dances” their way through a completely unscripted night fueled by crowd suggestions and fearless performances, no two shows are ever the same. Bold, unpredictable, and irresistibly funny, this one-of-a-kind live experience is a guaranteed crowd pleaser you won’t stop talking about. A show for all genders | 19+ only<span><br/></span>Warning: No extreme nudity, just extreme hilarity.<span><br/></span>
""";
