<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/33801ASNTMSCGCRRHSPSCJNKGBMBPNMSP>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Complaint Dept. and Lemonade";
  schema:description """
	<h1> Complaint Dept. and LemonadeThings Aren't Soup-Erb</h1><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>COMPLAINT DEPT. AND LEMONADE<span><br/></span>CSOPA’s JR Stage Performance class (ages 8-11) Demonstrates how People will complain about anything — not almost anything, but absolutely anything! In this rapid succession of hysterical grievances, the complaint department takes on everything from Oreo icing to kleptomania. From songs stuck in the head, to the price of cheese, and on and on and on. Could there be a glimmer of hope for anyone in charge of a complaint department?<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>THINGS AREN’T SOUP-ERB<span><br/></span>CSOPA’s Senior Devised Theatre class (ages 14-19) takes us to a surreal Soup-Topia with Things aren’t Soup-Erb. This show was written entirely by the students in the Senior Devised class. 200 years after a utopian island was created, things have gone a bit soupy in the pursuit of happiness. A small underground movement attempts to oppose the changes the Soup Cops have made, and it all comes to head when a nine-year-old boy goes to work with his dad.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>
""";
  schema:startDate "2025-05-20T19:50:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
