  schema:name "Crochet For Kids";
  schema:description """
	Ready to make something awesome with just yarn and your hands? Join our beginner crochet class for kids and dive into the world of creativity! Learn how to start with a slip knot, create a crochet chain, and bring your imagination to life. It’s fun, it’s hands-on, and you’ll love seeing your creations take shape!
