  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Crocheted Cup Cozy";
  schema:description """
	In this class for advanced beginners, learn how to make 3 different cup cozies, and how to change them up, and personalize them, by making color changes, or using different stitches in the color changes, for a different effect. Adjust the pattern to make it fit different sized cups/bottles/cans/etc and how to adjust the closure to make the cozy the right size.  
""";
