  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Crossroads Cabaret 2025";
  schema:description """
	<h1>Fortune awaits you at the crossroads... Are you bold enough to join us? </h1><span><br/></span>Step into a 19+ cabaret presented by Cirque des Morts Vaudeville Society and Chilliwack Cultural Center that celebrates the art of living authentically, featuring a mesmerizing blend of circus artists, dazzling burlesque acts, jaw-dropping drag performers, and so much more! Immerse yourself in an evening filled with vibrant colors, passionate performances, and a celebration of individuality that you won’t want to miss!
""";
