<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/97001ATRPSTQVHJMLQDBSQTNBMBDNNHSS>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Cupid's Comedy & Magic Show";
  schema:description """
	<h1>Looking for the perfect date night this Valentine’s Day? </h1><span><br/></span>Join the Fraser Valley Magic Company for an unforgettable evening of romance, laughter, and mind-blowing magic!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Hosted by the hilarious and charming comedy duo Norden & Gordon, this special Valentine’s edition features a lineup of three amazing, award-winning acts — guaranteed to make you fall in love with magic all over again!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Featuring the incredible illusions and comedy of Chris Yuill, a master of sleight of hand and mischief!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Plus, the award-winning husband-and-wife duo Trevor & Lorena, blending love, laughter, and world-class magic in a show that’s as heartwarming as it is hilarious!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>This isn’t your average magic show — it’s a love-themed night of magical comedy that will have couples and friends alike laughing, gasping, and wondering, “How did they do that?!”<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Whether you’re celebrating with someone special or just out for a fun night with friends, this is the show that will make your Valentine’s Day truly magical!
""";
