  schema:name "Dance Honours Performance 2026";
  schema:description """
	<h1>Dance Honours Performance is the best of the best in Dance.  </h1><span><br/></span>Features Provincial Delegates as soloists and other award winners as soloists, duos, trio, groups in all genres of Dance|; Ballet, Modern, Jazz, Stage, etc.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Please come and support all these hard-working young dancers, from 6 to 20 as they strive for perfection in their chosen craft.
""";
