<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/96001ATDVLRTKLJNHLNKQRGVCMQBHMDTV>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Dark Jokes for Nice Folks";
  schema:description """
	A stand-up comedy show for good people who need a little dark humor now and then. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Steve Taddy’s Dark Jokes for Nice Folks comedy show is centered around, you guessed it, dark humor. These are jokes for people who have a dark sense of humor but who are also not terrible people (eg. no racists, or homophobic jokes here). Join us for an evening of hilarious jokes and look at the darker side of the world. These are jokes you’ll want to repeat to your co-workers and realize halfway through it’s probably not a good idea.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Steve Taddy is a Vancouver based comedian. He has toured all over Western Canada and was featured in Calgary's inaugural Craft Island Comedy Festival. In 2023 Steve released his debut album, Insufferable, now streaming.
""";
