<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/148001ARPTBTDPSTNSSMPCRTNJMJTCGLB>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "DBX-The Doobie Brothers Experience";
  schema:description """
	<h1>“DBX – The Doobie Brothers Experience” – is Canada’s premier tribute to The Doobie Brothers.</h1><span><br/></span>Look-a-likes of Tom Johnston and Pat Simmons with vocal similarities and soaring vocal harmonies, are the band’s hallmarks and the foundation to which their performance has been built. With over 240 years of collective professional experience in the 6 piece band today, their performances are as close to the real deal as you’ll ever get.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>With one of the most “game-changing” song catalogues in rock and roll history from the Tom Johnston era to the Michael McDonald era, “DBX” has evolved into a masterful celebration of The Doobie Brothers. All rock enthusiasts know the words to “China Grove”; “Long Train Runnin’ “; “What A Fool Believes”; “Black Water”; “Takin’ It To The Streets”, or “Minute By Minute” and many, many more.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>If you love The Doobie Brothers, then welcome to an evening with “DBX – The Doobie Brothers Experience”, and “Listen To The Music”…
""";
