<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/48801AQHMRLTRLKHTVVSGQHTMLHGKSGHS>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Derek Seguin";
  schema:description """
	<h1>Comedy super star Derek Seguin is touring Canada with his hysterical new show to celebrate his 20th year as a professional joke teller.</h1><span><br/></span>Derek’s two-time Juno nominated stand up is always a pure reflection of his dysfunctional life, but naturally seen through his “slightly” twisted looking glass. This show will feature more of his hilarious stories on the challenges of relationships with his girlfriend, his three nearly grownup children and everyday life in a mixed-up world that he finds peculiar at best. With barely a moment to catch your breath between laughs there is never a dull moment in Derek’s shows and for 20 years audiences have loved him for it, but he loves you more!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>One of CBC’s The Debaters’ fan favorites; people are often surprised at the raw nature of Derek’s standup and how short he is. If you haven’t seen him live before; come out and discover the many hilarious surprises that his in-person shows are renowned for. No subject is off limits and no rabbit hole too deep.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>*Please be advised this performance contains frequent use of strong language and is intended for mature audiences.
""";
