  schema:description """
	<h1>Mini Project Dance presents ‘Down on the Farm’</h1><span><br/></span>Come see Chilliwack's cutest, Barnyard animals. Dancers ages 2-4 will light up the stage with their bright costumes, smiling faces and TALENT. The future is bright and we can't wait to perform for you.
