<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/85001ACHBTGLCRSPQVKRGBQRNDRPNKCVN>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "East Coast Swing Dancing";
  schema:description """
	You know you’ve always wanted to try it – so what are you waiting for? Jump into east coast swing dancing! In this fun and supportive class you don’t need to come with a partner – we will all dance together! Bring your appropriate footwear (no boots or flip flops), your legs, and a sense of adventure. By the end of this three-hour workshop you will have covered the basics of rock-step, triple step, and Charleston. Learn simple turns, tricks, and kicks, and work on the foundational skills that make the dance look and feel good!
""";
  schema:startDate "2025-12-11T18:00:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
