<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/141801ABQGQJCGHNTPPTLKLSMKVMPTLQH>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Epidermis Circus";
  schema:description """
	<h1>Naughty, Hilarious, Hands Only, Vaudeville Puppet Show!</h1><span><br/></span>Watch an experienced television puppeteer create a live puppet film right before your eyes, using only everyday objects, a camera, and her bare hands. Ingrid Hansen (Fraggle Rock, Jim Henson Company, Sesame Workshop,) creates cheeky vignettes in the palm of her hand and projects them onto a giant screen. When her fingers move, they instantly come to life. She animates objects to invent comical characters: a mischievous baby, an endearing shark, a clementine doing a striptease... This sophisticated puppet cabaret offers a healthy dose of comedy and breathtaking illusions that will transport your mind to surreal worlds!  SPICY, FOR AGE 14+. <span><br/></span>
""";
