<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/109402AHMCPSMGTBCQKDMKNJDCVCLBGSS>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Family Crochet ";
  schema:description """
	Learn something fun with mom or dad or Nana and Papa! Start from the very beginning –learn how to create a slipknot, chain, single crochet, and double crochet, how to read a basic pattern, and how to create a granny square. They will learn how to turn the granny squares into a scarf, or small blanket, and how to incorporate different colors, as well as how to join them together, and do a single crochet edging.
""";
