<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/95401AGGBMPCTBRTDHHTVTLNKSQLNNNQC>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Family Snowball";
  schema:description """
	Get ready for a magical evening of festive fun at STAR 98.3’s Family Snow Ball, proudly presented by Otter Co-op! On December 3rd, the Chilliwack Cultural Centre will transform into a winter wonderland for families to come together, celebrate the season, and enjoy a special screening of the holiday classic Elf.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Before the movie begins, we’re rolling out the red carpet with exciting surprises and special guests to kick off the night in style. Come dressed in your holiday best or cozy pyjamas; this event is all about creating joyful memories together.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Tickets are just $5, and proceeds will support the Salvation Army Food Bank. Plus, for every non-perishable food item you bring, you’ll be entered into a draw for a Grand Prize, which will be announced right after the movie! The more items you bring the more chances you have to win AND the more our community benefits!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>It’s a night of laughter, warmth, and giving back—so gather the whole family and join us for an unforgettable evening at the Family Snow Ball!
""";
  schema:startDate "2025-12-03T18:30:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
