<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/178001AKCHMSVPVQMCBCVCMQMLGKNPCKR>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Fantasies for Two";
  schema:description """
	<h1>From Schubert’s Romantic Vision to Gershwin’s Jazz‑Inspired Fantasy.</h1><span><br/></span>The Bergmann Duo is delighted to present Fantasies for Two, a richly expressive programme celebrating the artistry and magic of piano four-hands performance. Sharing a single keyboard, the duo creates a sound of remarkable depth, intimacy, and dramatic power. The programme features Franz Schubert’s magnificent and deeply moving Fantasy in F minor, one of the most profound masterpieces in the piano duet repertoire. Completing the programme is Marcel Bergmann’s imaginative Fantasy on Gershwin’s Porgy and Bess, inspired by the music of George Gershwin. Together, these works create a compelling dialogue between Romantic depth and modern colour—an evening of musical storytelling, expressive nuance, and dazzling ensemble playing.
""";
