  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Flowers in Watercolour";
  schema:description """
	Join us as we explore the world of flowers using watercolour paint - a unique opportunity for students to explore new techniques in watercolour painting such as applying washes, wet on wet techniques, pouring, glazing and masking. The brilliant character of flowers will be examined.  Subject matter will include flowers in nature and in still life.
""";
