  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Glass Mosaic";
  schema:description """
	Unleash your creativity with vibrant, sparkling glass mosaics! Learn how to nip, chip, and score glass to design your own stunning piece. Discover the art of laying glass, perfecting grout lines, and finishing with the satisfying process of grouting and polishing. With expert tips and tricks, you’ll leave with a beautiful, one-of-a-kind masterpiece. No experience needed—just bring your creativity!
""";
