<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/170201ALQKMTRPGJHCJMKRJLVRPPCPHGL>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Hold On To Your Butts";
  schema:description """
	<h1>A wildly inventive blend of comedy, physical theatre, and live Foley in a laugh‑out‑loud parody of the greatest dinosaur film of all time.</h1><span><br/></span>Hold On To Your Butts is a wildly inventive stage sensation that turns the ultimate dinosaur blockbuster into a laugh‑out‑loud theatrical event. Fresh from critically acclaimed West End and Off‑Broadway runs, this smash hit features two fearless performers and a Foley artist recreating the film live, shot for shot, with razor‑sharp comedy, physical theatre, and ingenious sound effects. Fast, funny, and packed with jaw‑dropping creativity, it’s a non‑stop thrill ride that has critics calling it “painfully funny” and audiences roaring with laughter from start to finish.
""";
