<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/187201ATQTBPJHSKGGTCNKDVLSTDMSVGK>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Holiday Comedy Rumble";
  schema:description """
	<h1>Holiday Comedy Rumble: Every Elf for Themself</h1><span><br/></span>A hilarious comedy competition where you, the audience decide the winner!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Come watch Canadas’s best improvisers in this hilarious clash of comedy titans. The ultimate showdown with massive laughs – it’s Holiday Comedy Rumble!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>The 5-Star Rated Comedy Department has been wowing audiences at their sold-out comedy shows in Vancouver and the Lower Mainland and now they’re back in Chilliwack!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Grab your tickets now and make the Holiday Season easier this year by planning ahead!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>When Santa’s out of office, the elves throw down.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>This holiday season, trade in the same-old sugarplum routine for a night of razor-sharp holiday comedy. Holiday Comedy Rumble is coming to Chilliwack!
""";
