  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Holiday Harmonies";
  schema:description """
	<h1>Step Back in Time This Holiday Season with The Maybelles!</h1><span><br/></span>Get ready for a nostalgic celebration as The Maybelles present an unforgettable Christmas show, paying tribute to your favourite 1960s variety specials! This festive performance brings beloved Christmas classics to life with stunning harmonies and a whole lot of Maybelles holiday magic. And just like the old TV specials, you never know who might drop by... several surprise guests will be stopping in to join the fun!
""";
