<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/111601ABCPQMJQCGVRSGPJMMHHMGSPGSV>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "How a Mood Becomes a Moment";
  schema:description """
	Learn to communicate emotion through visual storytelling with our Artist-in-Residence Brooke Cote. Live demonstrations will illustrate key concepts in creating mood and feelings, followed by time to practice on your own using a curated set with a live model. Each student will have the ability to take a variety of photos, using creative thinking to achieve a variety of moods from a single set. Students must bring their own camera and note taking materials and have previous experience using a camera. This is not an introductory class.
""";
