  schema:priceCurrency "CAD" .

<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/89601AKRVVCJTBRTNVLJGHCGGBSNHMHQH>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Hungry for Laughs Comedy Tour 2025";
  schema:description """
	<h1>Canada’s Funniest Comedy Tour is rolling into town, and it's more than just a night of stand-up — it's a movement. </h1><span><br/></span>Founded by comedian Alex Mackenzie and proudly produced by Canadian-owned ECL Productions, the Hungry for Laughs Comedy Tour brings together the best comedians in the country for an unforgettable night of laughter, love, and giving back. Each show supports a local charity, so when you buy a ticket, you're not just treating yourself to world-class comedy — you're helping your community thrive. Whether you’ve seen us on Amazon Prime, Just for Laughs, or CBC’s The Debaters, you’re in for a night of big laughs and positive vibes in a room full of great people. Hundreds of hours go into producing each show — all to create a moment. And when you're in that moment, laughing alongside hundreds of people from your community, you're making memories with your loved ones that will last long after the curtain closes. If you love stand-up comedy, believe in giving back to your community, and enjoy supporting the rising comedic stars of Canada — this show was made for you.
""";
