<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/29601AVVVGLGMQTHTLNRNLGJBCQJTVHSN>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Improv Comedy Rumble";
  schema:description """
	<h1>A hilarious comedy competition where you decide the winner!</h1><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Come watch Canadas’s best improvisers in this hilarious clash of comedy titans. The ultimate showdown with massive laughs – it’s Improv Comedy Rumble!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>The 5-Star Rated Comedy Department has been wowing audiences at their sold-out comedy shows in Vancouver and the Lower Mainland and now they’re back for an encore performance in Chilliwack!
""";
