<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/171601AJGRQLNBBJVPJDNHVMRKHNNKGNG>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "International Guitar Night Canada 2027";
  schema:description """
	<h1>A breathtaking celebration of the guitar, featuring world‑class masters and global musical traditions.</h1><span><br/></span>International Guitar Night (IGN), the world’s premier acoustic guitar ensemble, proudly returns to Canada with an expansive nationwide tour in 2027. With deep roots in the country, having launched on the West Coast and maintained a strong presence for more than two decades, IGN is renowned for electrifying performances and consistently sold-out theaters. This world-class lineup of master guitarists from across the globe delivers a stunning, genre‑spanning experience, seamlessly weaving Brazilian rhythms, passionate Flamenco, evocative Middle Eastern melodies, and the infectious swing of Gypsy jazz. This unforgettable concert celebrates the guitar as a truly global voice, breathtaking, intimate, and exhilarating, and promises to captivate devoted fans and newcomers alike.
""";
