  schema:description """
	In this acrylics class, you'll learn how to compose and start a painting, beginning with an underpainting to establish light and dark tones. You'll then move on to mixing and applying vibrant colors, all with the goal of creating a finished, eye-catching piece. Perfect for beginners and those looking to refine their skills!
""";
