  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Intro to Embroidery";
  schema:description """
	Join us for a series of classes where you will learn about hoops, embroidery floss, and basic to intermediate stitches which can be used to create a finished piece of your own design. Students will learn how to transfer a pattern and  how to finish pieces for display in the hoop. 
""";
