  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Introduction to Crochet (11-13)";
  schema:description """
	In Introduction to Crochet, students will learn the basics of crochet and start creating their own projects. Whether they want to crochet scarves, toys, or other fun items, this class provides the foundational skills needed to get started in this timeless craft. Students will leave with the basic skills to crochet on their own and experiment with new patterns.
