<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/49801AVVVJQRDHHCHGRNLMSSLHRNCVBPM>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "L'Amour de la Musique";
  schema:description """
	A delightful benefit concert that is sure to enchant hits Chilliwack – L’Amour de la Musique, for the love of music<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>The Chilliwack Academy of Music is proud to present  L’Amour de la Musique, for the love of music benefit concert, a dazzling showcase of talent that highlights the extraordinary musical achievements of our Academy family, along with a selection of french-inspired hors d’oervres from the creative genius of Fresh Impressions chef Elizabeth Grimaldi. This benefit concert on June 14 at 5:30 pm at the Chilliwack Cultural Centre promises a delightful evening of captivating performances and delicious appetizers. This benefit supports outreach musical education in our community, and provides access to musical opportunities for children.
""";
