<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/161401AMDNMJMCRHJHLVDBRLSHQRCNKCG>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Latin Heat Live";
  schema:description """
	<h1>Celebrating the women who changed the sound of Latin music!</h1><span><br/></span>Susana Williams brings the vibrant spirit and powerful legacy of Latin women in music to the stage in an unforgettable live production. Featuring the iconic hits of Gloria Estefan, Shakira, Karol G, and Jennifer Lopez, this show shines a spotlight on the voices, rhythms, and stories that helped shape Latin pop across generations. Blending high-energy performance with rich musicality and heartfelt storytelling, Susana celebrates the artistry and cultural influence of the women who transformed the global music landscape.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Joined by an exceptional eight-piece band—featuring some of the finest musicians on the West Coast, including Chilliwack’s own Kyle Radomsky—Susana delivers a dynamic, immersive concert experience filled with rhythm, passion, and movement. From infectious dance anthems to powerful ballads, the show captures the emotional depth and electrifying joy of Latin music at its best.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>More than a tribute, this production is a celebration of identity, community, and the unstoppable force of women in music. Whether you grew up with these songs or are discovering them anew, this performance invites audiences of all backgrounds to share in a night of connection, culture, and pure musical excitement. A must-see event for Chilliwack and the Fraser Valley.
""";
  schema:startDate "2026-06-05T19:30:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
