<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/103803ACMPGLVKSSKHDHNMNPDLPTMJBHN>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Learn To Crochet (16+)";
  schema:description """
	Join your instructor as they guide young fibre artists though the ins and outs of crochet. Crocheting can be fun and relaxing! Start from the very beginning – learn how to start a project with a slip knot and crochet chain to crochet your very own granny square which can be the start of a dishcloth, pillow case or even a blanket. <span><br/></span>
""";
