<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/15201AJRGPHRLRVGVLSMBRKVQSJMVJBSH>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Legends Show";
  schema:description """
	<h1>\"Legends Show\" brings you some of North America's most exciting performers live on stage. Accompanied by the “Rockin’ Royals Band”, this show will feature the most incredible Tributes to Roy Orbison and Elvis Presley.</h1><span><br/></span>Performing as Roy Orbison, Jesse Aron, who hails from the State of Wisconsin, is recognized as one of USA’s top Roy Orbison Tribute performers. With his eﬀortless voice and uncanny resemblance to Roy, Jesse will take you back in time with such hits as ‘Crying’, ‘Pretty Woman’, ‘Only The Lonely’, ‘Running Scared’, and many more of your favourites.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Performing as Elvis Presley, Pete Paquette is a World-class Elvis Tribute Artist and highly regarded as one of the top Elvis performers in the business today. Known for captivating his audiences through his incredible voice, high energy, charisma, and playful spontaneity with his audiences, this multi-award-winning performer will leave you wanting more.
""";
