  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Melody & Martini";
  schema:description """
	This fundraiser brings the community together to support and nurture rising stars in classical music. Held in conjunction with Rising Piano Stars—taking place later that evening at the HUB International Theatre—this cocktail fundraiser offers a perfect blend of elegance and purpose. Guests will enjoy curated food and drinks, along with a live music performance that offers a glimpse of the musical excellence to come later in the evening at the Rising Piano Stars. A silent auction with curated items will further enhance the fundraising experience, adding both excitement and opportunities to give.
""";
