<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/174801AVTRQJMHSVVDHTBHGKGPTTNSKCM>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Mom's the Word";
  schema:description """
	<h1>The Hilarious Holiday Hit!</h1><span><br/></span>The moms are back in the creative kitchen and ready to turn the “season of giving” into the “season of forgiving.” Enjoy a theatrical feast flavoured with big Santa belly laughs, stuffed with dysfunction, and topped with a soupçon of sarcasm—all served on a platter of naked truth. Using their special recipe of raw humour and humanity, the moms prove that the holidays really are about family, however you define it. Six moms. Zero filters. Mom’s the Word: Talkin’ Turkey delivers smart, raw, holiday honesty about motherhood, family, and traditions gone wrong. Serving up raw laughs, brutal truths, and Christmas chaos, no sugar coating.
""";
