<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/56201AGSGSGJVVGPLSGRNJSLQQTTQHHRQ>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Moneka Arabic Jazz";
  schema:description """
	<h1>High-energy rhythms from Iraq and African groove meld with Jazz to create a new, indescribably sensational sound. </h1><span><br/></span>Rooted in Blues and Jazz, the ensemble’s unique sound comes from frontman, Ahmed Moneka’s Afro-Iraqi roots, reflecting his life and extensive stops between Baghdad and Toronto. Accompanied by undeniably skilled musicians, old tales and traditional instruments are transformed by inventive compositions!
""";
