<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/144201ACRJLPDPTMLBQNDHKDSSJGCDBHP>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Monsters of Rock Arena Tour";
  schema:description """
	<h1>Get Ready for the MONSTERS OF ROCK Arena Tour!</h1><span><br/></span>Prepare for a full-throttle night of arena rock as four powerhouse tribute bands hit the stage to deliver the ultimate rock and roll experience. This isn’t just a concert — it’s a high-voltage event packed with thunderous guitars, explosive energy, and the biggest anthems ever written.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Relive the glory of classic arena rock with spot-on tributes to legendary bands like AC/DC, Def Leppard, Kiss, and Mötley Crüe. From blistering riffs and soaring vocals to larger-than-life stage presence, this show brings the sound, look, and attitude of rock’s greatest icons back to the stage.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>If you love big hooks, loud guitars, and the raw power of classic rock performed live, this is the show you don’t want to miss. Grab your friends and get ready to rock the night away as the Monsters of Rock tear up the arena!
""";
