<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/38001AJMJGLMVGBGPDQNMJJMCJDLNBDQB>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Music Honours Performance";
  schema:description """
	Featuring the Best of the Best of these young musicians from 6 to 22 years old and includes:<span><br/></span>Performers from all soloists and groups going forward to Represent Chilliwack at the Provincials in Victoria in early June of 2025.<span><br/></span>Also, Overall many Winners and Honourable Mentions from Piano, Strings, Classical Voice, Musical Theatre, Choral and Hopefully Band are also featured.
""";
