<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/139801AGNQKSSLKVSMPHSBQDBKDDRVSGH>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Music Honours Performance 2026";
  schema:description """
	<h1>Music Honours Performance is the best of the best in Music.  </h1><span><br/></span>Features Provincial Delegates as soloists and other award winners as soloists, duos, choirs and bands in all Specialties in Music; Piano, Strings, Classical Voice, Musical Theatre, Woodwinds, etc.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Please come and support all these hard-working young musicians, from 6 to 28, as they strive for perfection in their chosen craft.
""";
