<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/175801ALMMVRGTHQGGLPNVQMLDJRDHMNR>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Music That Smiles";
  schema:description """
	<span><br/></span><h1>Music That Smiles with the Bergmann Duo and guest violinist Cameron Wilson.</h1><span><br/></span>This is a lighthearted and entertaining program filled with wit, charm, and playful surprises. The Bergmann Duo are joined by guest violinist and composer/arranger Cameron Wilson, featuring his delightful works Hiccup di Tango and Pink Panther Variations. The program also explores humour in works by some of the great classical composers, bringing joy to life through imaginative music that is sure to leave audiences smiling.
""";
