  schema:description """
	Learn to refine your skills at the drawing characters, facial expressions, body shapes, and colour composition. Over the course of six weeks, explore the different types of character designs in anime and their Japanese terminology. Work with pen and ink to construct and develop your manga illustrating skills and bring your characters to life!. Previous anime experience required.
""";
