<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/68002ABHBGCQNCNLNNKHSKQGLSDRVDJVJ>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Old Songs, New Songs";
  schema:description """
	<h1>Old meets the new with this romantic piano concert!</h1><span><br/></span>Explore the timeless beauty of classical and romantic with The Bergmann Duo and Old Songs, New Songs. Together with violinist and UBC professor, Ryan Davis, the Bergmanns will stun audiences with pieces such as “Schubert’s Litany for the Feast of All Souls” and Fauré’s ever-popular “Après un Rêve.” paired with some iconic songs from the popular music realm
""";
