<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/3760ARRMKGNMHCSHHTMPMJHJRTGDQDDMN>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Ole!";
  schema:description """
	<h1>Inspired, electrified, and virtuosic, The Bergmann Duo return with a Spanish flare!</h1><span><br/></span>This joyful and energetic programme will feature an array of works that showcase the notable influence of Spanish music on various composers of the 19th and 20th centuries. From Bizet’s beloved opera Carmen to Lecuona’s Malagueña and music by the American Jazz icon Chick Corea, this concert promises to leave you invigorated and inspired!
""";
