<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/34801AJDHTGHVDDDGHKMHBRJLKTRHLMSR>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "On Wednesdays We Wear Black";
  schema:description """
	<h1>\"On Wednesdays We Wear Black\" is a bold, theatrical dance experience inspired by the hit Netflix series Wednesday. </h1><span><br/></span>With a sensual, dark, twisty edge, the show brings Wednesday Addams’ world to life as she unravels mysteries, forges unexpected friendships, and faces dangerous foes at Raven University In a place where nothing is as it seems, who can she trust—and what lessons will she learn?
""";
