  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Our Town (8-11)";
  schema:description """
	How would you paint a picture of life in Chilliwack? What are your favourite places to see and things to do? Take classic Chilliwack vistas and recreate them using art techniques and upcycled materials. When registering your child, please indicate which child will be attending in the order notes. Please note that we have updated requirements for registration, behaviour policy, accessibility limitations, and student waivers.
""";
