<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/170601AJGCRVPVJNKGBKCLJMVRQQDPCSC>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Peking Acrobats";
  schema:description """
	<h1>The Peking Acrobats, A Gravity‑Defying Global Sensation!</h1><span><br/></span>Experience an exhilarating spectacle of breathtaking skill and artistry with The Peking Acrobats. From daring feats atop towering chair pagodas to gravity-defying tumbling, contortion, trick cycling, and astonishing foot juggling, the performance is a stunning kaleidoscope of strength, precision, and grace. Enhanced by vibrant costumes, live musicians playing traditional Chinese instruments, and dazzling special effects, the show unfolds with the excitement and pageantry of a Chinese Carnival. Now returning to North America for their Gala 30th Anniversary Tour, The Peking Acrobats continue a centuries-old tradition of excellence, bringing fresh innovations and unforgettable new acts to the stage. Audiences, old and new, should prepare for a truly extraordinary entertainment experience.
""";
  schema:startDate "2027-05-01T14:00:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
  schema:image <https://system.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/files/cdf75021-2a50-4731-86a6-6e43393a918d.jpg>;
