<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/45001APSKGSQJNQPLCLJCBDHPHSDJVPSS>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Pine Needle Basket Weaving";
  schema:description """
	Discover the traditional craft of pine needle basket weaving and create your very own piece of Indigenous art! In this class, you’ll learn how to weave pine needles into a sturdy and beautiful basket. Using simple techniques, you’ll stitch together these organic materials, creating a functional and decorative piece to cherish. Perfect for beginners, this class is a calming, creative way to connect with nature while making a piece of art that’s both beautiful and useful.
""";
