<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/132001ARHNMVSVKDJKMJVTHCPDQNKNRQM>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "PWRUP - AC/DC TRIBUTE";
  schema:description """
	<h1>Chilliwack! Get Ready to Rock</h1><span><br/></span>PWR/UP is heading to HUB International Theatre to bring you the ultimate AC/DC experience.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>This is ain't your grandpa's pub band. Our lineup is packed with raw energy and youth, channeling AC/DC in their prime. Front man John Kairis delivers the power and grit of Bon Scott and Brian Johnson, bouncing between their iconic styles to give you the authentic AC/DC sound you have been waiting for.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Get ready to hear the classics like you remember them, loud, tight and true to the album. Do not miss it!
""";
