<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/174401AQSTQHDKHJJHHNTVDNCCLJGQGJG>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Revival";
  schema:description """
	<h1>REVIVAL is a high-energy dance production presented by Spencer Studios.</h1><span><br/></span>A celebration of the music that has soundtracked generations, dance floors, late nights, and unforgettable moments.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>The songs you never skip.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>The ones that still hit.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>The ones that take you somewhere the second they start.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>From iconic classics to unforgettable anthems, REVIVAL is inspired by the tracks people know, love, and instantly connect with.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Because some songs don’t stay in the past.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>They come back louder.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>18+ Event
""";
