<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/142201ADSMQMNCDGVRHQGNHPNKQQPPBDL>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Rocky Horror Picture Show";
  schema:description """
	<h1>Give yourself over to the Time Warp, where weird is wonderful.</h1><span><br/></span>Join us for a screening of The Rocky Horror Picture Show, the legendary cult‑classic musical that turns movie night into a full‑blown celebration. Bursting with campy humor, unforgettable songs, and outrageous characters, this wild blend of sci‑fi, horror, and rock‑and‑roll follows a young couple whose quiet road trip detours straight into glorious chaos. Famous for its interactive midnight screenings, costumes, and enthusiastic sing‑alongs, Rocky Horror isn’t meant to be watched quietly, it’s meant to be experienced. Whether you’re a longtime superfan or a curious first‑timer, come ready to laugh, sing, and give yourself over to the Time Warp.
""";
