<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/8401ACDNQDNDVRQCTJQRQPHVTKLNTCVJH>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Ronstadt & Totally Twain";
  schema:description """
	<h1>Two Iconic Entertainers (Linda Ronstadt & Shania Twain) & Two World Class Tributes (Totally Twain & Classic Ronstadt).</h1>Shania Twain & Linda Ronstadt are two Iconic entertainers who between them have sold over “200 million albums” and have 19 Grammy awards between them. They also have numerous awards and accolades which are too numerous to name. They are the first two superstars of Country & Pop that happen to be female! Totally Twain is Canada’s #1 Shania Twain tribute featuring vocalist Michelle Reid backed up by her all-star band. Totally Twain is authentic and provides a classy Shania experience like the “Queen of Pop” herself! This show will not disappoint. Dazzling costumes, nostalgic moments and audience participation. Classic Ronstadt (The Legacy of Linda) is fronted by D.L. Car who also is the front person for the Heart Tribute, Barracuda. Her band consists of some of the elite musicians on the Pacific West Coast. Classic Ronstadt are honored to be performing the amazing music catalog of songs which have made Linda Ronstadt one of the first female superstars of pop and Country.
""";
