<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/134401ABMHBQRNTQPLSNSHMVGCVJDRQGP>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Rotary Pianomen";
  schema:description """
	<h1>Pianomen is an electrifying musical tribute to two of the greatest songwriters of all time, Billy Joel and Elton John.</h1><span><br/></span>Led by the talented Peter Tam on piano and vocals, the show features an ensemble of skilled musicians on bass, drums, guitar, sax and keyboard, offering a one-of-a-kind musical extravaganza that takes the audience on a journey through the iconic songs of these legendary musicians.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>With a repertoire that spans several decades, The Pianomen offers a diverse selection of timeless classics and upbeat dance tunes that will have you tapping your feet and singing along. The performers’ energy and passion are palpable as they bring these beloved songs to life with their unique style and interpretation.
""";
