  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Sew a Sweatshirt";
  schema:description """
	In this course, you will sew a dropped-shoulder hoodie tailored to your size. You’ll learn how to measure your body, use sewing patterns, cut fabric, and sew with knit materials. The hoodie features a lined hood and ribbing at the hem and cuffs. 
""";
