<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/106402AGNPPKSHCJTVMKMSLTHTVLLNLGJ>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Smart Phone Photography for Adults";
  schema:description """
	Get the most out of your smart phone photos! Come and learn more about the core mood building tools from our Artist in Residence, Brook Cote! Tools such as framing, light and shadow, colour, expression, and movement will be explored as well as the free apps you can use to edit and filter your photos. Hands-on demonstrations and creative activities prepare photographers for a session of live practice and sharing of your fun experimentation at the end of the workshop.
""";
