<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/148801AKNBDJDJRNBDDKTKPMNJMHCPTHN>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Sophie's Surprise";
  schema:description """
	<h1>Strap In for a Wild Ride of Dazzling Circus Mayhem!</h1><span><br/></span>Sophie’s Surprise 29th is explosive, exhilarating, and impossible to resist. Packed with jaw‑dropping acrobatics, sharp comedy, bold theatre, and pulse‑racing aerial feats, this fast‑moving spectacle delivers nonstop thrills. Capturing the electric anticipation of a surprise party about to unfold, the cast draw you in from the very first moment. This is no ordinary celebration, it’s an all‑out theatrical extravaganza bursting with drama, magic, music, comedy, and sky‑high energy. Gravity‑defying aerial work on ropes, hoops, and ribbons dazzles and thrills, leaving audiences gasping and cheering. Sophie, a very lucky audience member, experiences a surprise party she’ll never forget… and neither will you.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Please be aware this show contains audience participation, partial nudity, haze, flashing lights, strong language and general idiocy.
""";
  schema:startDate "2026-10-26T19:30:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
