<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/32001ABCGNLKMHMQDQQTTRQRNTSNGPVMC>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Stand Back";
  schema:description """
	<h1>Stand Back: Stevie, Christine & Fleetwood Mac with Stan Giles Band on Valentine’s Day!</h1><span><br/></span>Join us for an unforgettable evening at the Chilliwack Cultural Centre as we pay tribute to the legendary Stevie Nicks, Christine McVie, and the timeless music of Fleetwood Mac. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Relive the magic of their iconic hits in a captivating performance that celebrates their enduring legacy. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Opening the show is Chilliwack’s own Stan Giles Band, setting the stage with their dynamic energy and local charm. Don’t miss this night of extraordinary music and heartfelt homage!<span><br/></span>
""";
