<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/159801AQJGSDJTQVMCTKMGBCTGNVBGVNL>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Sto:lo DrumMaking";
  schema:description """
	We are pleased to bring a Stó:lō artisan to the Centre as they teach students how to make a traditional hand drum.  <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Join them as they share their drum making skills and teaches some of the history and stories of the Stó:lō people. Students will be led in making a hide drum and will also take home a drum stick.  
""";
