<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/165801AMPBBHMMPDBQDKJVBBVHJRKDPKH>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Stuart Little";
  schema:description """
	<h1>A Big Adventure for One Very Small Hero.</h1><span><br/></span>Celebrating the 75th anniversary of its first publication, Stuart Little, adapted for the stage by Joseph Robinette, brings E.B. White’s timeless classic vividly to life. Intimate, imaginative, and full of heart, this delightful production invites audiences of all ages into a world where courage comes in the smallest packages. Stuart, an endearing little mouse with a very big heart, navigates a world built for humans, racing toy sailboats, retrieving treasured rings, and bravely rising to every challenge. When his beloved friend Margalo is frightened away by the scheming family cat Snowbell, Stuart sets off on a heartfelt journey that celebrates friendship, family, and perseverance. Charming and adventurous, STUART LITTLE is one little big adventure the whole family will love.<span><br/></span>
""";
  schema:startDate "2027-03-23T16:00:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
  schema:image <https://system.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/files/b1c6a306-2ec6-4d8e-9f0a-3dbd4c02edd7.jpg>;
