<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/136201AVHBTQNGRLTPQMVTBTCBNBHTPPS>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Super Spring Concert";
  schema:description """
	<h1>The Chilliwack Community Band, under the direction of Maestra Paula DeWit, is thrilled to invite the public to a lively and uplifting Spring Concert.</h1><span><br/></span>This fun-filled evening will showcase a delightful selection of great concert band tunes, perfect for welcoming the season with energy, melody, and community spirit. Audiences can look forward to timeless favorites and engaging arrangements that highlight the band’s signature blend of enthusiasm and musical excellence.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>For over three decades, the Chilliwack Community Band has brought people together through the joy of music, welcoming musicians of all ages and skill levels—no auditions required.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Join us for an evening of great music, smiles, and spring vibes!
""";
