<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/71201AVSGMKVRTJBLJQHRLCDKPBMVPLSB>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Symphony of Emotion";
  schema:description """
	<h1>Internationally acclaimed Trio Fibonacci brings together violin, cello and piano, in a spellbinding programme!</h1><span><br/></span>Trio Fibonacci returns for another exciting concert; A Symphony of Emotion – Beethoven Meets Einaudi! Discover a new adaptation of the symphony for piano trio - a reminder of the days when large-scale works were performed in condensed form in the comfort of one’s own living room. Debuting in 1998, Trio Fibonacci internationally recognized for their brilliant interpretations of the entire piano trio repertoire, having performed around the world! Join us for another splendid atmospheric concert as the music of Ludovico Einaudi takes audiences on a journey of intimacy and pure melodies.
""";
