<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/140801ACTKGTJVVSMJRNPRBPJNCTRJNCT>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "The 2026 Sporty's Awards!";
  schema:description """
	<span><br/></span><h1>The Sportys™ are an awards program like no other, recognizing all the finest local athletes, coaches, teams, and supporters for their incredible achievements in 2025.</h1><span><br/></span>We’re thrilled to be able to showcase all the amazing talent encompassing all that is sport, in Chilliwack.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Anyone who played in a sport in 2025, in Chilliwack, is eligible for nomination.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>YOU get an opportunity to impact the results. NOMINATIONS ARE ON NOW until February 13.  Nominate and vote for your favourites in one of 8 major categories, once per day – more details on the voting site.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Ice ’n’ Snow Awards<span><br/></span>Aqua Awards<span><br/></span>Pitch ’n’ Turf Awards<span><br/></span>Track ’n’ Trail Awards<span><br/></span>Courtside Awards<span><br/></span>In-the-Ring Awards<span><br/></span>Get Your Motor Running Awards<span><br/></span>The Superstars Awards<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>On February 16, the FINAL FIVES will be announced on social media, for each category!  Voting then commences for these Final Fives until March 13.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>On March 20, all the winners will be announced, onstage, at the beautiful Chilliwack Cultural Centre in an unforgettable evening of entertainment, helmed by Chilliwack Comedian and “talker guy”, Cliff Prang!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>It’s more than just an awards show, it’s an entertainment event showcasing schools, clubs and Chilliwack performers.<span><br/></span>
""";
  schema:startDate "2026-03-20T19:00:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
