<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/95001AGRTJLQSRDPVNBKJLGDDCGQSBRRT>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "The Art of Banned Books";
  schema:description """
	The Chilliwack Cultural Centre is hosting our first ever Right 2 Read Night! Join us for a powerful discussion of “Chains” by Laurie Halse Anderson. Read the book, bring your thoughts, and be a part of the conversation.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>We’re currently experiencing an unprecedented book-banning, affecting more books than at any time in North American history. Its main targets are books by and about people of color and members of the LGBTQ+ community. At Right 2 Read Night, we celebrate the freedom to read. Let the power of words inspire and captivate you during this special event.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Join us for a community conversation and tell us why books like “Chains” matter!
""";
