<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/89401ATPRKKNMKCBDQNCVHVDCMGJRDGGR>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "The Art of Halloween";
  schema:description """
	<h1>The Art of Halloween is a vibrant celebration of music, creativity, and spooky season flair — all in support of the Chilliwack Arts & Cultural Centre Society.</h1><span><br/></span>The evening begins with cocktails at 6:30 PM, where guests can mingle and soak in the festive atmosphere. Then, the spotlight turns to The Valley Babes, who take the stage with an enchanting and comedic cabaret performance full of charm and theatrical flair.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>At intermission, guests can indulge in delicious pizza before gearing up for the costume contest, where one lucky winner will take home a prize package that includes two tickets to Josephine and a $100 gift certificate to Bow & Stern in District 1881.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>After the costume contest winner is crowned, the evening winds down with a final spooky performance by The Valley Babes. Then, guests can hit the floor for a DJ-led dance party that keeps the Halloween spirit alive — all wrapping up by around 10:00 PM, just in time to leave you thrilled, not tired.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Whether you're there for the music, the costumes, or the community vibe, The Art of Halloween promises a night of festive fun and artistic expression.
""";
