<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/154401ADQDKNDGVMGCPBVSVTHJJDSNDNL>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "The Art of Modern Boardgames";
  schema:description """
	<h1>Featuring a thoughtfully curated board‑game lineup from our resident enthusiast!</h1><span><br/></span>Step into a world where dice tumble like shooting stars and every table holds a tiny adventure waiting to unfold. Choose from an assortment of delightfully curated board‑games—each lovingly selected by our resident enthusiast. Settle in, scheme a little, laugh a lot, and play your way toward victory. Triumph might just earn you vouchers that can be traded for charming prizes, but the real treasure is the journey you take along the way.
""";
