<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/15601ATMPBSJPVHGDQLTKHTGJDDNPRJJP>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "The Art of Reading";
  schema:description """
	<h1>Step into a world where literature and elegance intertwine at The Art of Reading, an enchanting event designed for book lovers and tea enthusiasts alike. </h1><span><br/></span>Imagine a cozy, high tea setting adorned with china, soft lighting, and the soothing aroma of freshly brewed tea. <span><br/></span> <span><br/></span>As you settle into your seat, you will participate in a book selection process, its title and author concealed. This “blind date” with a book invites you to explore new genres and authors without preconceived notions, adding an element of surprise and excitement to your reading experience. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Throughout the event, you’ll enjoy an assortment of delectable desserts, finger sandwiches, and a selection of teas to choose from. Engage in lively discussions with fellow attendees, share your thoughts on your mystery book, and perhaps even discover a new favorite author.  <span><br/></span>
""";
