<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/118601ALPCMHJNQGBRCQPPCJSKTMSSSBV>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "The Best of John Williams";
  schema:description """
	<h1>Experience the legendary symphonic world of John Williams with music from Star Wars, Jurassic Park, Indiana Jones, E.T., Jaws, Superman, Schindler’s List, and more!</h1><span><br/></span>“The Music of John Williams” is an unforgettable concert and audiovisual experience for all age groups, film enthusiasts, music lovers, and families. The greatest film scores of all time will be performed by the Hollywood Film Orchestra in a breathtaking show. Star soloists from renowned stage productions will bring to life iconic themes, including menacing moments from Jaws and the sweeping adventure of Star Wars.
""";
