<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/3756AJJRPPBGVLRCTDRLQRQQKCBKVSNQR>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "The Debaters Live";
  schema:description """
	Join host Steve Patterson and two of the country’s top comedian debaters, Yumi Nagashima and Charlie Demers, for a night of stand-up comedy and hilarious debate. Watch them go toe-to-toe in a battle of facts and funny with the audience picking the winner! These shows aren’t recorded for broadcast, so don’t miss out on a once-in-a-lifetime event. Having a great time is not up for debate!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>The Debaters Live on Tour is the comedy stage show where comics go toe-to-toe in a battle of laughs and logic and the audience picks the winner. Award-winning comedian and host, Steve Patterson brings two of Canada’s top headlining stand-up comics, Yumi Nagashima and Charlie Demers, to venues across Western Canada to delight crowds with an exhilarating exchange of facts and funny.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>But that’s not all.  Before Steve launches into the debate portion, The Debaters Live on Tour gets the hilarity rolling with segments of smart stand-up comedy from all three of these world-class comics.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>The Debaters Live on Tour features two debates in the format familiar to fans of the popular radio show The Debaters. Program creator and tour producer, Richard Side, is excited to present this extraordinary line-up that will leave audiences debating their favourite punch-lines.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>These all-new comedic clashes are for live audiences only and will not be recorded for broadcast. No two live shows are ever alike so get your tickets now for a once in a lifetime experience.
""";
