<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/54801ALMQKJGDVBDJQKPLMBMQRRRSMCNM>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "The Golden Anniversaries";
  schema:description """
	<h1>A Canadian play bursting with life and love.</h1><span><br/></span>Each year since their marriage, Sandy and Glen Golden have celebrated their anniversary at the same cottage for a romantic getaway. This upcoming 50th anniversary marks a special milestone in their blissful marriage; the only issue? Sandy’s cancelled their big anniversary party and kicked Glen to the curb. Join the Goldens as they humorously recount the good, the bad, and the ugly of spending half a century together. From the writer of Bed and Breakfast and The Birds and the Bees, The Golden Anniversaries is a comedy-drama about marriage, memory, and long-term love for the ages!
""";
  schema:startDate "2026-03-17T19:30:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
  schema:image <https://system.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/files/25ecf5bb-9112-4bdb-bc1a-9fb3edd32194.jpg>;
