<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/175001ATLMKKJGSKRRVMVMLPCJPTDGGQM>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "The Gordon Lightfoot Tribute Show";
  schema:description """
	<h1>If You Could Read My Mind: The Gordon Lightfoot Tribute Show.</h1><span><br/></span>“Listen to the band… this is NOT Gordon Lightfoot…. It is John Paul Byrne, singing Gordon Lightfoot! Most people thought this promo was from Gordon Lightfoot live albums.\"<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Singer-songwriter, artist John Paul Byrne pays tribute to the legendary Gordon Lightfoot in the much-lauded If You Could Read My Mind: The Gordon Lightfoot Tribute Show. Byrne is known for his uncanny ability to channel Lightfoot’s rich baritone and poignant storytelling, an experience that feels like stepping back into the intimate concert halls of the 1970s.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Having captivated audiences across BC and Alberta with sold-out performances, this Gordon Lightfoot Tribute Show has been celebrated for its authenticity and emotional depth, drawing comparisons to Lightfoot’s original performances. One reviewer noted, “Totally stunning, masterful and entertaining! Difficult to come up with enough superlatives to describe it.” From beloved classics like “Beautiful” and “Early Morning Rain” to the evocative ballad “The Wreck of the Edmund Fitzgerald,” Byrne’s performance is a heartfelt homage to one of Canada’s greatest musical icons.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Among the highest praises is a glowing endorsement from Steffan Clements, son of the late Terry Clements, who was Lightfoot’s lead guitarist for over four decades. “You just sang ‘If You Could Read My Mind’ better than anybody I’ve ever heard,” praises Clements.
""";
  schema:startDate "2026-07-10T19:30:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
  schema:image <https://system.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/files/df0dec3a-9241-4fc0-b952-57725dc2e9d7.jpg>;
  schema:location <https://spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/location/4201ASVGBHHRTVLQBSRVKDQCKNHHDCTSJ>;
  schema:offers _:1290a8eb9d794355b3e34223272b36868416;
  schema:keywords "Tribute Band";
  schema:duration "PT60M";
  schema:endDate "2026-07-10T20:30:00"^^xsd:dateTime .

