<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/24001ABMNLGCGVMRMGTMJKPBQCNHQQLMH>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "The Legendary Powder Blues";
  schema:description """
	<h1>TOM LAVIN & THE LEGENDARY POWDER BLUES For over four decades Powder Blues has been Canada’s leading blues band. </h1>The mix of swing, blues, jazz, rock & roll and R & B has an appeal so wide that people from seven to seventy swing side by side at a Powder Blues concert. Over the years the band has toured non-stop through Canada, the United States and overseas, spreading feel-good music that makes folks dance and shout. 
""";
  schema:startDate "2025-11-21T19:30:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
