<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/3705ABSHMSVRRDRHDHQGNTHTCHNKVSRJM>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "The Lightning Thief";
  schema:description """
	<h1>This year, CSOPA’s Mainstage cast presents The Lightning Thief: The Percy Jackson Musical, an adaptation of the beloved children’s book The Lightning Thief by Rick Riordan.</h1><span><br/></span>Percy Jackson, a young boy with ADHD and Dyslexia, is trying his hardest to be a good kid. Despite his best efforts, it seems like catastrophe follows him wherever he goes. When a monster attacks Percy at school –getting him expelled AGAIN – he learns that he is the son of a Greek god, or as the others call it, a Half-Blood. Nothing is as it seems anymore, not even his best friend, Grover. Suddenly, Percy is faced with new powers he can’t control, frightening prophecies he doesn’t want to decode, and a mythology textbook’s worth of monsters on his trail. 
""";
  schema:startDate "2025-01-25T14:00:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
