<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/118401ANKLDPVTKGKRJCKLCCSDNRTPTRL>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "The Music of Hans Zimmer";
  schema:description """
	<h1>Join us for an unforgettable concert event as a pirate from Pirates of the Caribbean leads you through the iconic scores of Hans Zimmer!</h1><span><br/></span>From Dune to James Bond, The Lion King, Gladiator, The Dark Knight, Inception, Interstellar, and more – this captivating performance features a film orchestra, choir, guest soloists, and exclusive film clips!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Don’t miss this once-in-a-lifetime musical journey. Secure your tickets now and immerse yourself in the epic soundscapes of Hans Zimmer!
""";
