<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/142401APTVNLQVQRLKMQNBSHQLSMKJDJL>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "The Nutcracker";
  schema:description """
	<h1>A World of Wonder Awaits in Ballet Victoria’s The Nutcracker.</h1><span><br/></span>Presented by Ballet Victoria, a festive favourite returns to sprinkle the season with magic, wonder, and a few delightful surprises each year. Brimming with the graceful artistry of the Ballet Victoria dancers, this enchanting production captivates audiences of all ages. When the Nutcracker Clara receives springs to life, she is swept into a charming dreamscape filled with swirling snow, fantastical lands, and unforgettable characters. Set to Tchaikovsky’s iconic score and brought to life through imaginative choreography and sumptuous costumes, The Nutcracker is a joyful celebration of the holiday spirit. Don’t miss this enchanting classical ballet when Ballet Victoria returns to the Chilliwack stage and let the magic begin.
""";
  schema:startDate "2026-12-19T19:30:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
