<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/3888AVGSSRPRNKBBNSBSGTKTMRBRTJQHK>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "The One and Only";
  schema:description """
	<h1>Beethoven wrote only one opera, Schumann only one piano concerto, and Saint-Saëns wrote the dazzling, delightful, and unique Carnival of the Animals.</h1><span><br/></span>Come and be awe-struck by these distinctive musical gems! The Chilliwack Metropolitan Orchestra will be joined by Chilliwack star Dr. Boris Konovalov on piano to perform Schumann’s Piano Concerto.
""";
