<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/96401ASLTRVQCVSCQKJTSLCGKRVTLKMSD>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "The Passion of Amy Winehouse";
  schema:description """
	<h1>\"Back to Black: The Passion of Amy Winehouse\" is a mesmerizing tribute that has captivated audiences and critics alike, celebrating the profound artistry of the late Amy Winehouse. </h1><span><br/></span>At the heart of this production is Saskatchewan's own Heidi Munro, whose dynamic stage presence and emotive vocals are widely known in Canada and breathe new life into Winehouse's timeless repertoire. Munro's portrayal has been lauded for its authenticity, depth and at the same time being a fresh, timeless and inviting interpretation. The American Federation of Musicians 553 acclaimed the show as \"a spectacle worthy of any stage in Vegas,\" underscoring the high caliber of the performance.
""";
  schema:startDate "2025-09-28T19:30:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
