<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/101202AVMDMBLKPVJRNTLCVKPRRBMDHSD>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "The Secret in the Wings";
  schema:description """
	<h1>Directed by Anna Griffith, The Secret in the Wings by Mary Zimmerman is the second production of UFV Theatre’s 2025-2026 season.</h1><span><br/></span>Presented by the UFV School of Creative Art’s Acting and Production Classes, The Secret in the Wings is a masterwork in theatrical story telling. The play is woven from obscure and unsettling fairy tales that explore the dangerous, mysterious, and often haunting undercurrents of childhood.
""";
