<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/92001ACMVVRHKQMSLNPTJRKSCQLCJBRDB>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "The Spy Who Sassed Me";
  schema:description """
	Dance meets danger in this outrageous spy-dance comedy! The Spy Who Sassed Me follows Sassy Powers, a high-heeled secret agent on a globe-trotting mission to recover her stolen Glowjo and restore sass to the world. A glitter-charged adventure packed with Heels dancing, wickedly camp villains, and femme fatales who own the stage.
""";
