<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/3924AJCRQJQDGGNVVJJQVVNLSCMBQNQQK>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "The Three Musketeers";
  schema:description """
	<h1>DuffleBag Theatre’s shows are all about fun, innovation, and joyful participation!</h1><span><br/></span>Want to join the bravest crew in all of France to protect the King? Young country lad D’Artagnan sure does and has trained his whole life to become a Musketeer. But he discovers it’s not so simple in DuffleBag’s adaptation of the timeless Alexandre Dumas adventure! Upon his arrival in Paris, D’Artagnan gets into trouble with Porthos, Aramis, and Athos, the very Musketeers he wants to join! When he stumbles upon Cardinal Richelieu’s secret plot to take the throne, only Constance, the Queen’s lady-in waiting, can help him save the King and stop the dastardly plot once and for all!
""";
