<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/59201ANQRMQQHPMKRBHKNCGQLPCVGCBKN>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "The Very Big Show";
  schema:description """
	<h1>One night. Two acts. Endless surprises.</h1><span><br/></span>Get ready for a night of big laughs, unbelievable magic, and nonstop entertainment. The Very Big Show unites two powerhouse performers for one epic event.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>SIMON KING is a stand-up juggernaut with rapid-fire wit, bold material, and a presence that takes over the room. Featured on HBO, Comedy Central, Just For Laughs, and praised by legends like Robin Williams.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>WES BARKER is a comedy magician known for insane tricks, hilarious storytelling, and viral energy. Seen on Big Trick Energy, Penn & Teller: Fool Us (which he won), AGT, Ellen, and more — with over 1 billion views online.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>It’s stand-up. It’s magic. It’s unforgettable.<span><br/></span>One ticket. Two stars. Zero dull moments.
""";
