  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "The Yo Show";
  schema:description """
	<h1>A premiere stand-up comedy celebration starring Ivan Decker, Kevin Banner, Katie-Ellen Humphries, Damonde Tschritter, Syd Bosel, Ola Dada, Nic Enright-Morin, Jan Bannister and Cliff Prang (host).</h1><span><br/></span>As seen on late night with Conan O’Brien, Canada’s Got Talent, Netflix, Just for Laughs, CBC’s Debaters, Winnipeg Comedy Fest, et cetera.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>The Yo Show is a top talent stand-up comedy show to raise funds and honor the legacy, vision & family of Chilliwack's greatest comedy community champion, Yo Trieu, by bringing fistfuls of Canada's Top Comics under one roof for an unforgettable night of non-stop laughs.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Yo Trieu - May 30, 1979 - August 1, 2025 <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>All costs for the venue, the comics, the marketing etc, have been covered. Every dollar goes to support the Trieu’s children.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>18+ Event<span><br/></span>
""";
