  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Urinetown the Musical";
  schema:description """
	In a gritty, Gotham like city suffering through a 20-year drought, a severe water shortage has forced the government to ban private toilets. Everyone must use public facilities controlled by a single corrupt corporation that charges admission for one of life’s most basic needs. When the people have finally had enough, an unlikely hero sparks a rebellion to win back their freedom.
""";
