<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/177801ATGGBLKVDRTLQTSPRKHJLRNHSTR>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Vancouver Cello Quartet";
  schema:description """
	<h1>Vancouver Cello Quartet: Redefining the Sound of the Cello.</h1><span><br/></span>With a dynamic stage presence and boldly innovative programming, the Vancouver Cello Quartet has earned a reputation for reimagining the possibilities of the cello, seamlessly blending classical tradition with contemporary flair. Featuring four of Vancouver’s most accomplished cellists, this remarkable ensemble brings a fresh and compelling perspective to chamber music, performing intricate, expressive arrangements that span centuries of repertoire. Let the rich, resonant voices of four cellos fill your afternoon with passion, sophistication, and musical brilliance.
""";
  schema:startDate "2026-09-09T19:30:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
