<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/18401APQBVKHJSJNGJQKHRTGTLCTRJBBR>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Walk Right Back";
  schema:description """
	<h1>From the producers of UK’s smash hit show That’ll Be the Day, this phenomenal production tells the story of the most successful musical duo of all time – The Everly Brothers. </h1><span><br/></span>Featuring hits such as Bye Bye Love, All I Have to Do Is Dream and Cathy’s Clown, this unique concert-based musical entwines the wonderful, sad yet glorious story of The Everly Brothers.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>With “harmonies from heaven” that influenced The Beatles, The Beach Boys, and Simon & Garfunkel, The Everly Brothers were unmatched in their talent. Also featuring songs from a couple of the Everly Brothers' good friends, Buddy Holly and Roy Orbison. This is a show not to be missed!<span><br/></span>
""";
