<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/83801ACBGJJMLLQRJQDMLGBDBQLGSCCJN>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Watercolour Beginnings";
  schema:description """
	Immerse yourself in the fluid beauty of watercolour with our beginner-friendly course! This class offers a relaxed and interactive setting where you'll explore essential techniques, from basic washes to wet-on-wet methods. Experiment with color and form as you bring a range of subjects to life. Join us and let your creativity flow with every brushstroke!
""";
