<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/104001ANLGQGDJQDKNBTPRVMHMPNMLBQP>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Wheel 3: Building Bigger";
  schema:description """
	Are you looking for your next ceramic challenge? Learn how to create larger pieces on the pottery wheel! This class will build upon a basic ceramic skill set and further your proficiency as a potter. Topics covered include throwing larger, multi piece vessels, lidded pots, pouring vessels, altered forms and basic surface decoration. Each class will begin with a specific skill demonstration followed by guided practice and support from the instructor. 
""";
