<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/48201AHQBKMVGJSTQGDDLBHBMNSLMGSVN>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Winter Harp 2025";
  schema:description """
	<h1>Magnificent music and festive stories come together for an evening of Christmas cheer!</h1><span><br/></span>Experience the festive splendor of Winter Harp, a beloved, unforgettable holiday concert. Rich medieval attire, backdrops of cathedrals, and a hauntingly beautiful selection of music immerse audience members in a heart-warming atmosphere. Paired with a world-class, eight-person ensemble of harps, flutes, rare medieval instruments, and singing, this performance is a journey into the heart of Christmas -- a place of joy, hope and light.
""";
