<http://www.spektrix.com/chilliwackculturalcentre/event/36401AGDPLVGNCJMRKTPQLBSBLCVKVSMG>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Wire and Crystals (Youth)";
  schema:description """
	Step into a world of mystical energy with Wire & Crystals! In this class, teens will explore the beauty and power of natural crystals, learning how to incorporate them into unique jewelry pieces. Each crystal holds its own energy, from the calming properties of amethyst to the empowering strength of clear quartz. Students will choose their favorite crystals and create custom pendants, connecting with the stones’ meanings while crafting something beautiful and personal. This is the perfect opportunity to design a piece of jewelry that reflects your own unique energy and creativity, and by the end of the week, you’ll walk away with a stunning, hand-made piece of crystal jewelry to wear or gift!
""";
