  schema:name "Yuki the Juggler";
  schema:description """
	<h1>A High‑Energy Japanese Juggling Spectacle with Tradition, Comedy, and a Show‑Stopping Finale!</h1><span><br/></span>All the Way from Japan is a high‑energy, interactive juggling spectacle blending traditional Japanese artistry with modern circus skill. Fresh from touring the world, Yuki the Juggler delivers a captivating mix of precision juggling, cutting‑edge object manipulation, comedy, and audience participation, creating a performance that is lively, playful, and unpredictable. Inspired by Edo Daikagura, a 400‑year‑old Japanese performance tradition, the show seamlessly fuses heritage with contemporary flair. Yuki’s charismatic stage presence and comedic timing create a strong connection with the crowd as the excitement builds toward a jaw‑dropping finale. Culturally rich and wildly entertaining, All the Way from Japan delivers thrilling circus energy, unforgettable skill, and a finale audiences won’t soon forget.
""";
